Dry weight basis
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 means reporting chemical analysis results by excluding the weight of the water in the sample. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

