Liquid PCBs
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 means a homogenous flowable material containing PCBs and no more than 0.5 percent by weight non-dissolved material.

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Low exposure areas
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 mean all areas 0.1 kilometer or greater distant from a residential commercial area (as defined in 761.123) and areas
other than ``high exposure area'' as defined elsewhere in this section. 
