Microencapsulation
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 means the stabilization of debris containing PCBs with the following reagents such that the leachability of any associated
PCB is reduced to specified levels: Portland cement or lime/pozzolans (e.g. fly ash and cement kiln dust). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=37 g=1 f=1 -->
*&blank;&blank;*&blank;&blank;*&blank;&blank;*&blank;&blank;* 
