<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Non-liquid PCBs
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 means PCBs which contain no liquids which pass through the filter when using the paint filter test method (EPA Method
9095 in ``Test Methods for Evaluating Solid Waste'' (SW&hyph;846)). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

