<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Open burning
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 means the combustion of any PCB regulated for disposal, not approved or otherwise allowed under part 761, subpart
D of this part, and without the following: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) Control of combustion air to maintain adequate temperature for efficient combustion. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) Containment of the combustion reaction in an enclosed device to provide sufficient residence time and mixing
for complete combustion. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) Control of emission of the gaseous combustion products. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=37 g=1 f=1 -->
*&blank;&blank;*&blank;&blank;*&blank;&blank;*&blank;&blank;* 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
