Remediation site or site
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 means the areal extent of contamination and all suitable areas in very close proximity to the contamination necessary
for implementation of a cleanup of PCB remediation waste regardless of whether the site was intended for management
of waste. 
