certifying the accuracy of the information submitted. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(B) A record of the registration for each PCB Transformer at each location (e.g., a copy of the registration and the
return receipt signed by EPA) must be retained with the records of inspection and maintenance for each PCB Transformer
required under 761.30(a)(1)(xii). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(C) The requirements identified in paragraphs (a)(1)(vii)(A) of this section must be complied with to continue the
authorization for use or reuse of PCB Transformers under 761.30, pursuant to section 6(e)(2)(B) of TSCA. 
