) of this section and left on site shall have residual levels of: Less than or equal to 25 ppm as in paragraph (a)(4)(ii)(A)(
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
1
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
) of this section; less than or equal to 50 ppm, and the area shall be secured by a fence, and a sign, including the ML shall
be posted, as in paragraph (a)(4)(ii)(A)(
