<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
(j)
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
 Changes in ownership or operational control of a commercial storage facility.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 The date of transfer of interim status or final approval shall be the date the Regional Administrator (or Director,
Chemical Management Division) provides written notice of such transfer. The Agency will recognize the transfer
of interim status or final approval for commercial storage facilities if all the following conditions are met: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) The transferee demonstrates it has established, by the date of transfer, financial assurance for closure pursuant
to paragraph (g) of this section using a mechanism effective as of the date of final approval so that there will be no
lapse in financial assurance for the transferred facility. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(2) The transferee submits a new and complete application for final storage approval including all the elements listed
in paragraph (d) of this section. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) The transferor or transferee resolves any deficiencies (e.g., technical operations, closure plans, cost estimates,
etc.) the Agency has identified in the application of the transferor. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

